The,Mozilla,Mobile,Messaging,WebSMS,API,simplifies,the,integration,of,tools,that,implement,messaging,concepts,in,web,content,Once,integrated,in,applications,the,API,facilitates,the,exploitation,of,create,send,and,receive,message,properties,in,web,content,in,addition,to,manipulating,the,SMS,and,the,MMS,functionalities,The,API,s,mobile,browser,support,is,currently,restricted,to,Firefox,Mobile,Gecko,and,Firefox,OS